<p>After being bombarded with questions from fans, Molly-Mae went on to share a lengthy video explaining exactly what had happened. </p>

<p>The YouTuber began: 'Right excuse the fact that I look like a Stig of the Dump this morning but all of you want the juicy gossip on why the neighbours hate us so guess what I'm going to give it to you... </p>

<p>'It's going to be a massive let down by the way. Like it's a really boring story but here we go anyway. So it's all to do with recycling! Told you. Yeah told you it was going to be a massive let down.'</p>

